OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tue 9 Jun to Thu 18 Jun
OL,6,FChangeable early in this period with
OL,7,FAtlantic frontal systems moving across
OL,8,Fthe UK. These will bring showers or
OL,9,Flonger spells of rain at times, with
OL,10,Fwettest conditions in the northwest,
OL,11,Fdrier in the southeast. Strong winds
OL,12,Fmay affect parts of the UK at times,
OL,13,Fespecially the northwest. Later in the
OL,14,Fperiod, higher pressure and more
OL,15,Fsettled conditions may begin to become
OL,16,Fmore prevalent, especially in the
OL,17,Fsouth. There will probably still be
OL,18,Fsome wet interludes though.
OL,19,FTemperatures are likely to be near to
OL,20,For a little above normal overall.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
