OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Fri 19 Jun to Fri 3 JulFThe
OL,6,Fstart of the period is likely to be
OL,7,Frelatively settled for most of the UK.
OL,8,FHigh pressure is likely to be in the
OL,9,Fvicinity of the UK bringing drier
OL,10,Fconditions, especially to the south
OL,11,Fand east. However some showers or
OL,12,Fspells of rain are still possible,
OL,13,Fparticularly in the north and west.
OL,14,FWinds will mostly be light with
OL,15,Ftemperatures probably above normal and
OL,16,Fit could be hot at times in the south.
OL,17,FTowards the end of June, low pressure
OL,18,Fmay begin to have more of an
OL,19,Finfluence, especially across the south
OL,20,Fwhere heavy showers and thunderstorms
OL,21,Fbecome more probable.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
